dataList.title: T Corp.
dataList.content: Away, ya gits. This one’s ours!

dataList.title: T Corp.
dataList.content: Looks like you lot are running low on time as well… tough luck! We’ve only got thirty minutes ourselves!

dataList.title: T Corp.
dataList.content: Oi, maybe they’re one of the Dead Rabbits or somethin’.
Thirty minutes? Thirty minutes for what?

dataList.title: T Corp.
dataList.content: Ain’t possible. The old Dead Rabbits and their vigilante ways are no more… All they do nowadays is starin’ at ya funny from behind those odd masks.

dataList.title: T Corp.
dataList.content: Bollocks, we don’t got time for this… let’s kill 'em quick!
They began rushing at us with bloodshot eyes, not giving Heathcliff time to even finish his sentence.
